headline: Fiserv Publishes 2024 Thanksgiving Holiday Spending Insights
summary: MILWAUKEE, December 06, 2024--Fiserv, Inc. (NYSE: FI), a leading global provider of payments and financial services technology, has published a special report detailing consumer spending growth during the 2024 holiday shopping season.

headline: Fiserv cuts as many as 1,500 employees, analyst estimates
summary: The payments processor confirmed it had eliminated jobs. A Wolfe Research analyst estimated the reduction may impact as much as 3.7% of the workforce.
